org.objectfabric

Class TMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.objectfabric.TObject
      • org.objectfabric.TMap<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Map<K,V>

    public class TMap<K,V>
extends TObject
implements java.util.Map<K,V>
    Transactional map. For each thread this class behaves like an HashMap, except:

    - It does not support null keys.
    - It does not implement clone.
    - Entries do not support setValue(V).

    See comments on TSet about iterators and concurrency, methods that both read and write, and exceptions.
